==References== {{refbegin}} * Church, Alfred John. Brodribb, William Jackson (Trans.) (1876). ''Annals of Tacitus''. MacMillan and Co. * Frost, Percival (1872). ''The Annals of Tacitus''. Whittaker & Co. * Simek, Rudolf (2007) translated by Angela Hall. ''Dictionary of Northern Mythology''. [[Boydell & Brewer|D.S. Brewer]]. {{ISBN|0859915131}} {{refend}}
