[[File:Tejakembang.jpeg| thumb |The native Crossing river at Cibeet river, in Tejakembang, Cijeruk, [[Dayeuhluhur, Cilacap | Dayeuhluhur]], Cilacap Regency]] '''Cibeet River''' is a river in [[Dayeuhluhur, Cilacap|Dayeuhluhur]], [[Cilacap Regency]], [[Indonesia]].
==Geography== The river source is at [[The Forbidden Forest of the Upper Cibeet River]], Dayeuhluhur Mountain. Two important [[tributaries]] of this river are [[Cikawalon River]] and [[Cidayeuh River]].
Its mouth is where it merges into Cijolang river at Bingkeng village.
Cibeet River has the purest river water in [[Cilacap Regency]], because it comes from a dense and undeveloped tropical forest. [[File:Cibeet5.jpeg|thumb | Cijolian waterfall One of a sacred place at Cibeet River]]
==Keeper key== This river has a Keeper key''' '''([[juru kunci]]) for guarding its spirituality. In Dayeuhluhuran (Sundanese Religion), this river is sacred. The key is held by Ceceng Rusmana.
